  "datePublished": "2026-03-01",
  "description": "The representamen is the form a [sign](./sign.md) takes — the mark, sound, gesture, image, or token that enters into a [sign](./sign.md) relation. It is the thing that does the representing, as distinct from the object it represents and the [interpretant](./interpretant.md) it produces.",
